'''雷恩加角'''（{{lang-en|Cape Reinga}}，{{lang-mi|Te Reinga 或 Te Rerenga Wairua}}），[[新西兰|新西兰]][[北島_(紐西蘭)|北岛]]西北部[[奥普里半岛|奥普里半岛]]的最西北端，位于最近城镇[[凯塔亚|凯塔亚]]以北100公里。“雷恩加”（{{lang|en|Reinga}}）一词来源于[[毛利语|毛利语]]，意为“[[阴间|阴间]]”。<ref>[http://www.doc.govt.nz/conservation/historic/by-region/northland/kaitaia/cape-reinga/ Historic Cape Reinga] {{Wayback|url=http://www.doc.govt.nz/conservation/historic/by-region/northland/kaitaia/cape-reinga/ |date=20131203012117 }} (from the [[New_Zealand_Department_of_Conservation|DOC]] website)</ref>在[[毛利人|毛利人]]的信念中，雷恩加角是人死后的灵魂进入阴间的地方。<ref name="Nat">''[http://teaohou.natlib.govt.nz/teaohou/issue/Mao35TeA/c20.html Te Rerenga Wairua - Leaping Place of the Spirits] {{Wayback|url=http://teaohou.natlib.govt.nz/teaohou/issue/Mao35TeA/c20.html |date=20080907064859 }}'' - ''[[Te_Ao_Hou|Te Ao Hou]]'', No. 35, June 1961)</ref>

